headline: ‘In the trenches’: CH Robinson CEO shares views on tariffs, nearshoring
summary: The brokerage giant, heavily involved in U.S.-Mexico truckload crossings, is focused on helping customers navigate potential changes in cross-border trade, CEO Dave Bozeman said.
